Are you enjoying your time on the server so much that you'd REALLY like to help?

Would you like to help contribute to the server and get even more perks for it?

If you donate $500 USD or more, then you will get the Gold Supporter rank. This grants you a gold name in chat, even more chunk claims and the knowledge that you helped keep the server running by helping pay for the electricity costs, Internet bill and hardware upgrade/fix costs.

You also get access to the trashcan (icon in inventory) and /trash_can command. Yay?

Thank you for supporting us.
